License Notice
==============

This repository contains the research-code implementation for HiCR-Mamba.

The newly added HiCR-Mamba model components and project-specific files are
provided by Jianing Long for academic research use under the MIT License terms
below.

Parts of this repository are adapted from the PatchTST supervised forecasting
framework:

  PatchTST: "A Time Series is Worth 64 Words: Long-term Forecasting with
  Transformers" (ICLR 2023)
  Official repository: https://github.com/yuqinie98/PatchTST

Please also respect the license and citation requirements of PatchTST and its
upstream dependencies. If you require a codebase with no PatchTST-derived
framework files, refactor the training loop and data loaders before
redistribution.

